Linear is used for issue tracking across UW engineering.

Telecom org team prefixes:
- `TELX-` — Telco XP (Digi squad): frontend-heavy, currently focused on Broadband Onboarding Tracker
- `TEL2-` — Telecom Squad 2: VOIP enablement, provisioning, migrations, operational work

Dumitru's handset work is separate from both squads for now. After v1 delivery the team folds into the broader telecom/mobile org.

**Why:** After delivery, Dumitru will work within this org structure — useful to know who's who and what they're working on.
